[[!tag security/fixed]]

   1. Choose **Applications**&nbsp;▸ **KeePassXC**.

   1. Choose **Tools**&nbsp;▸ **Password Generator**.

   1. Switch to the **Passphrase** tab.

      A very strong passphrase of 7 random words is automatically generated.

      <div class="caution">

      <p>It is impossible to recover your passphrase if you forget it!</p>

      <p>To help you remember your passphrase, you can write it on a piece of
      paper, store it in your wallet for a few days, and destroy it once
      you know it well.</p>

      </div>
